          <p>
            Payments for bookings are processed through the 9jastay platform to ensure
            secure transactions for both guests and vendors. When a guest completes
            a booking payment, the funds are securely held by the platform until the
            booking begins.
          </p>
          <p>
            Vendor payouts are released after the guest has successfully checked in to
            the booked accommodation. This policy helps ensure that guests receive the
            accommodation they booked while also protecting vendors from fraudulent
            reservations.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>


